<paragraph id="8BA136D1FF5C76ACFF08D6224ACEF7D6" blockId="129.[163,779,633,716]" pageId="129" pageNumber="546">
<emphasis id="B96AEAC3FF5C76ACFF08D6224B29F795" box="[163,285,634,655]" italics="true" pageId="129" pageNumber="546">Diagnosis:</emphasis>
The original description does not provide sufficient information for the identification of this species.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BA136D1FF5C76ACFF08D6A84AC4F63E" blockId="129.[163,778,752,804]" pageId="129" pageNumber="546">
<emphasis id="B96AEAC3FF5C76ACFF08D6A84B09F61F" box="[163,317,752,773]" italics="true" pageId="129" pageNumber="546">Distribution:</emphasis>
Only known from the 
<typeStatus id="54A58873FF5C76ACFDFDD6A848BDF61F" box="[598,649,752,773]" pageId="129" pageNumber="546">type</typeStatus>
locality in 
<collectingCountry id="F3097641FF5C76ACFF08D7574AD8F63E" box="[163,236,783,804]" name="Japan" pageId="129" pageNumber="546">Japan</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BA136D1FF5C76ACFF08D7104B85F168" blockId="129.[163,780,840,1138]" pageId="129" pageNumber="546">
<emphasis id="B96AEAC3FF5C76ACFF08D7104B3AF647" box="[163,270,840,861]" italics="true" pageId="129" pageNumber="546">Remarks:</emphasis>
No figures were provided in 
<bibRefCitation id="EF8F4B20FF5C76ACFDF5D7104931F644" author="Kishida K" box="[606,773,840,862]" pageId="129" pageNumber="546" pagination="1 - 9" refId="ref92381" refString="Kishida K. 1910. Supplementary notes on Japanese spiders. Hakubutsu-gaku Zasshi 118: 1 - 9." type="journal article" year="1910">Kishida (1910)</bibRefCitation>
, and according to his description, this species resembles 
<taxonomicName id="4C1E4D52FF5C76ACFF08D7DE4932F681" authority="(Bosenberg &amp; Strand 1906)" baseAuthorityName="Bosenberg &amp; Strand" baseAuthorityYear="1906" box="[163,774,901,923]" class="Arachnida" family="Linyphiidae" genus="Paratmeticus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="129" pageNumber="546" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bipunctis">
<emphasis id="B96AEAC3FF5C76ACFF08D7DE4B81F680" box="[163,437,901,923]" italics="true" pageId="129" pageNumber="546">Paratmeticus bipunctis</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EF8F4B20FF5C76ACFE6CD7DD48C8F681" author="Bosenberg W &amp; Strand E" box="[455,764,901,923]" pageId="129" pageNumber="546" pagination="93 - 422" refId="ref89262" refString="Bosenberg W, Strand E. 1906. Japanische Spinnen. Abhandlungen der Senckenbergischen Naturforschenden Gesellschaft 30: 93 - 422." type="journal article" year="1906">Bösenberg &amp; Strand 1906</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
, although no further details were provided to assert such similarity. According to the original description, the palps of ‘ 
<emphasis id="B96AEAC3FF5C76ACFEEAD7B94BDDF6ED" box="[321,489,993,1015]" italics="true" pageId="129" pageNumber="546">
Oe.’ 
<taxonomicName id="4C1E4D52FF5C76ACFEDDD7BA4BDDF6ED" authorityName="KISHIDA" authorityYear="1910" box="[374,489,994,1015]" class="Arachnida" family="Linyphiidae" genus="Oedothorax" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="129" pageNumber="546" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="japonicus">japonicus</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
might resemble that of 
<taxonomicName id="4C1E4D52FF5C76ACFF08D0584B11F10F" authorityName="Dahl" authorityYear="1901" box="[163,293,1024,1045]" class="Arachnida" family="Linyphiidae" genus="Erigonella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="129" pageNumber="546" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B96AEAC3FF5C76ACFF08D0584B11F10F" box="[163,293,1024,1045]" italics="true" pageId="129" pageNumber="546">Erigonella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from 
<bibRefCitation id="EF8F4B20FF5C76ACFEDFD0584826F10C" author="Denis J" box="[372,530,1024,1046]" pageId="129" pageNumber="546" pagination="673 - 675" refId="ref90510" refString="Denis J. 1964. Notes sur les erigonides. XXIX. Une forme pyreneenne d' Erigonella subelevata (L. Koch). Bulletin de la Societe Zoologique de France 89: 673 - 675." type="journal article" year="1964">Denis (1964)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation id="EF8F4B20FF5C76ACFDFDD0584937F10C" author="Strand E" box="[598,771,1024,1046]" pageId="129" pageNumber="546" pagination="22 - 30" refId="ref95576" refString="Strand E. 1905. Araneae. In: Report of the second Norwegian Arctic expedition in the ' Fram. ' Kristiania 3: 22 - 30." type="journal article" year="1905">Strand (1905)</bibRefCitation>
, but both these species were also described without illustrations. Therefore, the relationship of this species to other taxa is unclear.
</paragraph>
